    <item>
      <title>韩国警告朝鲜可能在美国大选前进行核试验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/south-korea-warns-north-may-do-nuclear-test-nearing-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国防部长表示，朝鲜可能考虑在美国总统大选临近时进行核试验，以提高其知名度，因为金正恩推出了能够打击美国及其亚洲盟友的新型弹头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/south-korea-warns-north-may-do-nuclear-test-nearing-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
