    <item>
      <title>以色列议会夏季休会缓解内塔尼亚胡的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会于周日休会三个月，为总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡提供一些国内喘息的机会，因为该国面临着对加沙战争的批评、提前举行选举的呼声以及真主党在戈兰高地发动的造成十几名年轻人死亡的毁灭性袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/israel-hamas-war-parliamentary-recess-takes-heat-off-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举开始投票，可能引发重大转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拉加斯，委内瑞拉（美联社）——委内瑞拉的投票站已开始，周日人们将进行总统选举投票，选举结果要么会导致政局发生重大变化，要么导致造成世界和平时期最严重经济崩溃的政策再延长六年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 04:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、日本、韩国希望在美国投票前巩固安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国承诺将全力保卫盟友日本和韩国，并与其签署协议，以在 11 月美国选出下一任总统之前巩固安全合作成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/us-japan-south-korea-look-to-cement-security-ties-before-america-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
